stories.title: Streak: giant among pygmies
stories.subTitle: Zimbabwe v Bangladesh, 4th ODI, Harare
stories.summary:
Zimbabwe, without ever convincing, levelled the one-day series by beating
Bangladesh by 14 runs
stories.byline: The Wisden Verdict by John Ward

stories.title: Streak and Ervine to the rescue
stories.subTitle: Zimbabwe v Bangladesh, 4th ODI, Harare
stories.summary: A determined sixth-wicket stand of 76 between Sean Ervine and Heath Streak rescued Zimbabwe from 79 for 5 and guided them to a respectable 242 for 8 in the fourth one-dayer against Zimbabwe at the Harare Sports Club
